1954;;The Angel Who Pawned Her Harp;;British;;Alan Bromly;;Felix Aylmer, Diane Cilento;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Angel_Who_Pawned_Her_Harp;;A beautiful blonde angel (Diane Cilento) arrives in Islington on a goodwill mission to soften the heart of pawnbroker Joshua Webman (Felix Aylmer). To raise money for her mission, she pawns her harp. Bringing out the best in the people she meets, she shows them the path down which their happiness lies.